                <html:p>For <fr:link href="/forest/001F/" title="Convergent Sequence" uri="https://andrewczezowski.github.io/forest/001F/" display-uri="001F" type="local">convergent sequences</fr:link> our intuitive notions of algebra and order hold. <html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\text {lim}\left (a\right )=a]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\text {lim}\left (a\right )=b]]></fr:tex>.</html:p></html:p>
                <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
                  <fr:frontmatter>
                    <fr:authors />
                    <fr:date>
                      <fr:year>2026</fr:year>
                      <fr:month>4</fr:month>
